Title : Martin Mork
Text : '''Martin Trygve Mork''' (20 May 1933 &ndash; 19 March 2017) was a [[Norway|Norwegian]] oceanographer.

He was born in [[Kristiansund]]. He became a professor of theoretical oceanography at the [[University of Bergen]] in 1972 and a fellow of the [[Norwegian Academy of Science and Letters]] in 1974.<ref name=snl>{{cite encyclopedia|title=Martin Mork|encyclopedia=[[Store norske leksikon]]|url=http://www.snl.no/Martin_Mork|language=Norwegian|accessdate=22 December 2017}}</ref>

